{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And many times, as coming out of the philantropene, you would have children waiting there for you just to bother you, or hit you, or throw stones.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's when my parents decided that I would discontinue my education, which was a very hard thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And not only for educational purposes, but I had my friends in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- but at that time, quite a few children, quite a few students, would leave school already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What I did then, then I started to learn some kind of a-- of a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] something that you do with your hand, either dressmaking-- I used to be-- I used to-- a trade, that's what I was thinking for.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I used to be good in sewing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I would sit home and do-- and sew dresses for my mother, sometimes for friends, for myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and at that time, in 1935 the situation became already serious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was the time when I remember my parents taking everything a little bit more serious and saying, wait a minute, Hitler is not going to go away that soon.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He's been now in power for two years and it doesn't look that he's-- on the contrary, he seems to be getting more popular as he goes on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And people-- already some people already started leaving Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Jews started leaving Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I think it was around 1935 that my parents realized that the situation was bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I would also like to mention that in 1933, when Hitler came in power, my oldest sister, who was married, her father-in-law had decided before Hitler came in power that he will not stay in Germany if he becomes the leader-- the Fuhrer, as they said in Germany.",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
